This plugin adds Highlighting Embedded-HTML tiddlers (application/x-aspx, application/x-ejs, application/x-jsp and application/x-erb) to the [[CodeMirror|http://codemirror.net]] text editor. It needs the latest [[CodeMirror plugin|$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror]] to be installed

>To enable the Embedded-HTML Highlighting ~AddOn, copy the following line and ''append'' it at the bottom of the ''require'' section in $:/config/CodeMirror<br>

>Then make sure that all entries except the last one within the ''require'' section end with a 'semicolon'<br>

<$macrocall $name="copy-to-clipboard-above-right" src='		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/mode/multiplex.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/mode/htmlembedded/htmlembedded.js"'/>

```json
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/mode/multiplex.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/mode/htmlembedded/htmlembedded.js"
```

>''Save'' and ''Reload'' your wiki to have the changes take effect
